Title: Decipher the Cacophony
Description:
This is far worse than I thought. It's as if they're feeding the corruption. Encouraging it. The dissonance growing louder and louder...

<Orweyna seems shaken, but not deterred.>

I can hardly hear anything else. My head is pounding. I... I need to see how far gone this land truly is.

$n. Bring me something from the Unseeming.
ObjectivesText: Collect 10 Discordant Essence from Discordant enemies in the Unseeming.
CompletionText: What have the nerubians done to this place?
RewardText: This is wrong. This is all wrong.
